name: GAP-mix
description:
融合模型，大部分为二次元模型，融合有少量 2.5D 和真实感模型。对雪糕、袜、裸足、低视角有一定的特化。

Merged model, with some specification for thighhighs, socks, barefoot, and low angle. Most merged models are anime models.

推荐画质提示词 Recommended quality prompts：

  • best quality, absurdres, masterpiece, extremely clear

推荐负向提示词 Recommended negative prompts：

  • (worst quality, low quality:1.4), greyscale, monochrome, dusty sunbeams, trembling, motion lines, motion blur, emphasis lines, text, title, logo, signature

  • 更清晰的图像 More clear images: (depth of field, bokeh, blurry:1.4)

  • 更二次元 More anime style: (abs, muscular, rib:1.2)

  • 配合 easynegative 等模型

对多数 LoRA/LyCORIS 模型有良好的兼容性

Good compatibility with most LoRA/LyCORIS models.
